title_bed_bats_review: Home in Chandpur · 2 bedrooms · 2 beds · 2 baths
listing_description:
Relax with the whole family or with friends at this peaceful place.

Comfortable rooms, common living space facilities including large smart LED tv with cable lines (Akash). Free WIFI. Free bathroom toiletries. Kitchen arrangements with dining area. Front baranda/patio. Grass front yard with barbeque setup. Roop top seating arrangement for lush green field view. Small swimming pool.

Happy stay.
